title: - we now maintain knowledge of the active notebook throughought the application
message:
- we now maintain knowledge of the active notebook throughought the application
- therefore, we now adjust prompts accordingly; do not relink if unnecessary…
- …and we display the default notebook in bold/italic.

Note that, in the absence of semantic rendering, and TypeFace being a presentation concept, the device's current UI may interfere with proper display.
